{"tid":413994,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門公路啲快相機真係製造交通意外","createTime":"2017-09-26T00:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T12:12:57.000Z","uid":46010,"like":69,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"6d04537de0260f8b8bd00367094a580b633c34e2","tid":413994,"uid":46010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:50:48.000Z","msg":"眾所周知屯門公路沿路<br />\n有不下十個白鴿籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次經過總會有一片紅燈海<br />\n最陰濕係落完斜冇耐<br />\n個個都由架車溜落去慳水慳力<br />\n唔比油都溜到成百<br />\n然後就整一部你嘆<br />\n突然全部車都收慢<br />\n收唔切就好易炒埋一疊<br />\n或者落腳慢少少<br />\n就已經可以望鏡頭笑然後等收信<br />\n行親屯門公路都好守規矩<br />\n琴晚11點左右行過屯市對出果一段<br />\n知果部機堅野已經金睛火眼<br />\n住70 un住個brake過<br />\n過到一半突然閃左一閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣我行中線係最前<br />\n後面左右線有兩部車都幾近我<br />\n唔知中邊部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 P仔 唔想加監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f41be0b6ca23d7f61ec0b013147cfc161a4039","tid":413994,"uid":21028,"like":144,"dislike":12,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:53:54.000Z","msg":"講完咁多廢話原來p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae146e60385513d48bc1f289c49e992fa3efcb6f","tid":413994,"uid":41695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:54:10.000Z","msg":"我都P仔 想知如果中左幾耐到會收信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad017b190b2a32e8072dc28399ff1f7a2eb2cd47","tid":413994,"uid":46010,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:57:12.000Z","msg":"[quote]講完咁多廢話原來p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/咁每個咁每個人都做過新手嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e06370390cc1b1bdbf13fa53aea5347987273c2","tid":413994,"uid":46010,"like":65,"dislike":4,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"r