 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw,機師日日開2百幾3百...140算咩"},{"pid":"3ef90fb8cd8b2f90e27deaacbfb982c286a28882","tid":413994,"uid":46010,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋p仔限70真係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上公路真係行70<br />\n巴士同泥頭都推你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當自己天生賽車手？<br />\n就係多得你呢種p牌仔唔少 當正自己車神<br />\n咪成鳩日炒車囉 你炒車又要撞到人<br />\n又要塞住條路 想死建議你跳海 唔好死都要累人累物</blockquote><br />\n而家新牌仔一定係路面炸彈嘅<br />\n話P仔成日炒車<br />\n淨係識一碌鳩打一船人<br />\n而家揸得耐就唔會炒嘅<br />\n的士佬日日揸十個鐘<br />\n都會香港腳發作啦<br />\n個牌多人幾年就好威咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16863f32f415c6aba648ef039065fea72835678b","tid":413994,"uid":59252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間入屯門我會行下路<br />\n多燈都快過屯公<br />\n轉車站條大直路間唔中有間警車之外<br />\n鏡頭又少 P果陣都踩90咁去"},{"pid":"de29c3fca7772d77964de25d99d44eca28f37d79","tid":413994,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繁忙時間入屯門我會行下路<br />\n多燈都快過屯公<br />\n轉車站條大直路間唔中有間警車之外<br />\n鏡頭又少 P果陣都踩90咁去</blockquote><br />\n下路有單車"},{"pid":"5459c20d6774a0b90b858e9324bbd6407a2d2a55","tid":413994,"uid":8112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋p仔限70真係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上公路真係行70<br />\n巴士同泥頭都推你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我多數都照行中線快線 入幾次機場都係咁"},{"pid":"c82a05cab122f8b734a111e54b5422e5636abf51","tid":413994,"uid":8112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋p仔限70真係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上公路真係行70<br />\n巴士同泥頭都推你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wan